snippet.title: Defenders of the Omniverse | Release Date Trailer
snippet.description:
Get ready for an epic adventure in "Defenders of the Omniverse!" Watch our Release Date Announcement Trailer and join us as we dive into a vibrant, 3D rogue-lite world filled with intense reverse bullet hell action.

Wishlist it on Steam: https://bit.ly/4bUsEuy

Press Kit: https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/1cwEPy9C5q_icf-RZUtzyL3d-3ej9NFcL?usp=drive_link
